# Incident Report

## Fields

- **ID**: unique identifier for each incident report.
- **Timestamps**: date and time of the incident occurrence and report submission.
- **Validation Constraints**: requirements for data integrity and accuracy.
- **Description**: detailed account of the incident. (Required field)

## Example

- **ID**: 12345
- **Timestamps**:
  - **Date Occurred**: 2026-04-19 12:50:06
  - **Date Submitted**: 2026-04-19 12:50:06
- **Validation Constraints**:
  - Must include all fields
  - ID must be a positive integer
- **Description**: An example description of the incident reported here.

## Notes

Ensure that all reports adhere to the above structure and contain all required fields.